                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d539">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72119/939</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MEV1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morgan</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-11-14T17:00:00-03:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 14, 1917, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 6.20 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Understand that Argentina desires to turn proposed congress of neutrals into
                    congress of Latin America and that Brazil and Uruguay have, gone so far as to
                    inquire what program may be.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_MEV1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Morgan</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
